short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Generate google calendar events through AI prompts.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Autocal.ai is a tool designed to expedite the creation of calendar events through AI-driven prompts. Users input any specifics about a meeting including details like subject, location, time, and participants and the system auto-generates a calendar template link that can be immediately populated into a calendar.
